gust 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"2019\u201320 season\">{{cite web | url = https://www.kicker.de/thomas-mueller-39317/spieler/dfb-pokal/2019-20/bayern-muenchen-14 | title = Thomas M\u00fcller | language = de | website = kicker.de | access-date = 8 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Totals!!343!!116!!54!!32!!113!!44!!11!!3!!521!!195!!\u2014\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career totals!!378!!132!!54!!32!!113!!44!!11!!3!!556!!211!!\u2014\n|}\n{{reflist|group=lower-alpha}}\n\n===International===\n\n====International statistics====\n{{updated|19 November 2018}}<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/vereine/39317/nationalspieler_thomas-mueller.html | title = Thomas M\u00fcller | language = de | website = kicker.de | access-date = 8 June 2018}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!colspan=3|[[Germany national football team|Germany]]\n|-\n!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|2010||12||5\n|-\n|2011||13||5\n|-\n|2012||13||0\n|-\n|2013||9||6\n|-\n|2014||15||10\n|-\n|2015||6||5\n|-\n|2016||15||5\n|-\n|2017||6||1\n|-\n|2018||11||1\n|-\n!Total!!100!!38\n|}\n\n====International goals====\n:''Scores and results list Germany's goal tally first.''<ref name=\"rsssf\">{{cite web|url = http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/thmueller-intlg.html|title=Thomas M\u00fcller \u2013 Goals in International Matches|publisher = RSSSF | date = 22 January 2019 | access-date = 5 October 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"NFT\">{{cite web|url=http://www.national-football-teams.com/player/36374/Thomas_Mueller.html|title=M\u00fcller, Thomas|publisher=National Football Teams|accessdate=26 March 2018}}</ref>\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! # !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1. || 13 June 2010 || [[Moses Mabhida Stadium]], [[Durban]], South Africa || {{fb|AUS}} || align=center| '''3'''\u20130 ||align=center| 4\u20130 || rowspan=5|[[2010 FIFA World Cup]]\n|-\n| 2. || rowspan=2 | 27 June 2010 || rowspan=2 | [[Free State Stadium]], [